kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: dependency-workflow-23-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: getweather
        template: getweather
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: city
            value: '{{{{ inputs.parameters.city }}}}'
          - name: date
            value: '{{{{ inputs.parameters.date }}}}'
      - name: suggestoutfit
        template: suggestoutfit
        dependencies:
        - getweather
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: weather
            value: '{{{{ tasks.getweather.result }}}}'
      - name: planoutfit
        template: planoutfit
        dependencies:
        - suggestoutfit
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: event
            value: '{{{{ inputs.parameters.event }}}}'
          - name: outfit
            value: '{{{{ tasks.suggestoutfit.result }}}}'
  - name: getweather
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: city
      - name: date
    http:
      url: "http://weatherapi.com/query"
      method: "GET"
      headers:
        - name: "Content-Type"
          value: "application/json"
      body: "{ \"city\": \"{{ inputs.parameters.city }}\", \"date\": \"{{ inputs.parameters.date }}\" }"
  - name: suggestoutfit
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: weather
    http:
      url: "http://outfitapi.com/suggest"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        - name: "Content-Type"
          value: "application/json"
      body: "{ \"weather\": \"{{ inputs.parameters.weather }}\" }"
  - name: planoutfit
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: event
      - name: outfit
    http:
      url: "http://planoutfitapi.com/plan"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        - name: "Content-Type"
          value: "application/json"
      body: "{ \"event\": \"{{ inputs.parameters.event }}\", \"outfit\": \"{{ inputs.parameters.outfit }}\" }"
